{"title":"俺妈来信夸食堂","authors":["李斌"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":8,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺妈来信夸食堂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺社办起了食堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老妈妈来信讲了又讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你媳妇也下地去劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再在家里做饭忙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈我也下了地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再坐在炕头上；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我娘俩一天劳动十五分，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋后收入一定强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不用再往家寄钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把钱存到人民银行。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张家口市414信箱  李斌"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}